Insider Activity


Individual




Peter J. Fluor



Mr. Peter J. Fluor is Independent Director at Anadarko Petroleum Corp., Independent Director at Cameron International Corp., Lead Independent Director at Fluor Corp., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Texas Crude Energy, Inc., a Member at All-American Wildcatters Association, a Member at American Petroleum Institute, Inc. and Member-Council of Overseers at Jesse H Jones Graduate School of Business. He is on the Board of Directors at Anadarko Petroleum Corp., Cameron International Corp., Fluor Corp. and The Welch Foundation. 
Mr. Fluor also served on the board at Devon Energy Corp. 
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Southern California and an MBA from the University of Southern California. 



