Peter J. Fluor, MBA

Age : 69Public asset : 13,714,309 USDLinked companies :  Anadarko Petroleum Corporation -  Fluor Corporation (NEW) 





Summary 



Mr. Peter J. Fluor is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Texas Crude Energy, Inc., a Member at All-American Wildcatters Association, a Member at American Petroleum Institute, Inc. and Member-Overseers Council at Jesse H Jones Graduate School of Business.He is on the Board of Directors at Anadarko Petroleum Corp., Fluor Corp. and The Welch Foundation. Mr. Fluor was previously employed as an Independent Director by Cameron International Corp.He also served on the board at Devon Energy Corp.He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Southern California and an MBA from the University of Southern California.



